{"tid":1518172,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發][講大話 爛啫啫]黑色直升機喺長沙灣上空停留","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:45:27.000Z","uid":14264,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"43b2c67044fdbf2557c4b51708f4193979b9c483","tid":1518172,"uid":14264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我坐係屋企 突然聽到直升機聲<br />\n都好近下<br />\n望出房嘅窗外<br />\n見到喺長沙灣協和小學上空附近<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOnRqZ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOnRqZ9.png&h=6c70a0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（👆🏻大概呢個位置）<br />\n有架直升機停留（我估計有半分鐘）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bEu8td4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbEu8td4.png&h=34d8218a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（最大聲持續有半分鐘 嚟唔切影低停個下 只係影到佢飛走）<br />\n<br />\n好驚 發生咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac0d7da2b9a2b1c29554db633e119ae43f9cbaf","tid":1518172,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=8bdf686b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=e2df3dc7\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioZnnstt8OVeiO3